                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17730421-97-victim886 t17730421-97-viclabel457"></join>: the bridle hung up in a stable; I saw it the 20th or 21st of February; I did not miss it till I saw it advertised in the paper; my master went up to the gentleman, and found the bridle; he is now in the country.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17730421-97-person888">
